{"tid":1506615,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"快啲入！九月罷課，政府處理嘅預想","createTime":"2019-08-26T00:41:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T12:52:38.000Z","uid":17873,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"385bba8655af2c2a3fc1a75f784cf374da9b0cfe","tid":1506615,"uid":17873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T00:41:31.000Z","msg":"鑑於政府打壓手法層出不窮，軍事恫嚇、白色恐怖皆未收到即時果效下，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">學生勢成下一星期開刀之選</span></strong>，故此，請大家一齊預想一下可能出現嘅情況及相關應對&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<strong>政府處理：</strong><br />\n- 教育局命令學校每日呈上師生出席紀錄<br />\n- 要求學校從嚴處理缺席學生<br />\n- 著令學校不得張貼任何政治印刷品、不得呼喊任何政治口號<br />\n- 呼籲學生互相舉報<br />\n- 警察駐校維持紀律<br />\n- 嫁禍校內老師慫恿罷課，製造白色恐怖<br />\n- 建制派發動「老豆送仔」，押年輕人去校園<br />\n- 打壓任何學生所舉行嘅政治集會<br />\n<br />\n<strong>學生應對：</strong><br />\n- 每日刪除通話、whatsapp紀錄"},{"pid":"bbb6a8ce5edb7dc78023fc7500e7d2c3bce8f3ed","tid":1506615,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T00:56:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"edf4cfc0346089f63782aaa4a8038508a280beee","tid":1506615,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T00:56:43.000Z","msg":"「圖」多個內地日文Twitter帳號惡意抹黑示威 並大量宣傳解放軍資訊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1506545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1506545</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5bf732a23c8ed6eaa93cf669fc8930cede68b832","tid":1506615,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T00:58:23.000Z","msg":"政府帶頭製造校園白色恐怖<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ac2d68d0f509505c04191e142b1454e4702e20d","tid":1506615,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-